'''Throm Loro''' was a [[Human/Legends|Human]] [[Gender/Legends|male]] native to the world of [[Cilpar]]. He was the founder of the [[Cilpari Resistance]] and husband of [[Elscol Loro]].

==Biography==
Throm Loro joined the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. He participated in the liberation of a number of [[Prisoner/Legends|prisoners]] held at an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] base on [[Endor/Legends|Endor]]. Throm saved a [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiee]] named [[Groznik]] from execution during the mission, an action which earned him a [[Life debt/Legends|life debt]] from the Wookiee. When the two returned to Cilpar, they led the [[Cilpari Resistance|resistance]] against the Galactic Empire until Throm was [[Battle of the Cliffs|killed]] in an Imperial raid on one of the resistance's hideouts.

Years later, [[Mrlsst Trade and Science Academy]] rogue [[Scientist/Legends|scientist]] [[Rorax Falken]] used a [[Mrlssti Laser Phantoms|Mrlssti Laser Phantom]] image of Loro to obtain the services of Groznik.

